<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle3"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle3">* Define  the Lorenz equations </Text-field>
<Text-field style="_cstyle3" layout="_pstyle3"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L5" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">f1 := (x,y,z) -&gt; sigma * (y - x);</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">f2 := (x,y,z) -&gt; -x * z + r * x - y;</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">f3 := (x,y,z) -&gt;  x * y - b * z;</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">DE1 := diff(x(t),t) = f1(x(t),y(t),z(t)):</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">DE2 := diff(y(t),t) = f2(x(t),y(t),z(t)):</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">DE3 := diff(z(t),t) = f3(x(t),y(t),z(t));</Text-field>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="_pstyle7">DE := DE1, DE2, DE3;</Text-field>
</Input>
